# Application Building Context

Read the following files in order before implementing or making any architectural decision:

1. `context/project-overview.md` â€” product definition, goals, features, and scope
2. `context/architecture-context.md` â€” system structure, boundaries, storage model, and invariants
3. `context/ui-context.md` â€” theme, colors, typography, canvas design, and component conventions
4. `context/code-standards.md` â€” implementation rules and conventions
5. `context/ai-workflow-rules.md` â€” development workflow, scoping rules, and delivery approach
6. `context/progress-tracker.md` â€” current phase, completed work, open questions, and next steps

Update `context/progress-tracker.md` after each meaningful implementation change.

If implementation changes the architecture, scope, or standards documented in the context files, update the relevant file before continuing.

