  - Suppressed default browser drag behavior using a transparent 1x1 GIF drag image for a unified visual experience.
- [x] Node resizing and inline double-click label editing (feature-spec `14-node-editing.md`)
  - Added `<NodeResizer>` in `CanvasNodeRenderer` to show subtle brand-colored handles and outlines on selected nodes.
  - Implemented custom double-click on node labels to toggle an inline textarea editor.
  - Configured textarea with `nodrag nopan nowheel` classes to prevent canvas interference, auto-growing height, and placeholder support.
  - Connected label editing to real-time `onNodesChange` flow using `setNodes`.
  - Wrapped canvas `onNodesChange` callback to intercept `dimensions` updates and synchronize them to the node's `style.width` and `style.height` via Yjs/Liveblocks `replace` changes, supporting both new and persisted node states.
- [x] Chevron shape and shape-specific safe boundaries for text overflow prevention
  - Replaced the `triangle` node shape with `chevron` (arrow/process block) across the schema types, node renderer, bottom toolbar, and drag previews.
  - Defined custom `SAFE_ZONES` padding/insets mapping absolute positioning bounds for all 10 shapes (e.g. circle, diamond, cylinder, chevron).
  - Placed labels and inline textareas inside these safe zones to prevent labels from overflowing the visual borders.
  - Added the `break-all` class to labels and textareas to force long words to wrap cleanly.
- [x] Bugfixes, hydration, performance, and lint cleanup
  - Fixed HTML hydration mismatch in `ProjectSidebar` where project items had buttons nested inside buttons. Converted outer elements to accessible `div`s with `role="button"` and keyboard navigation.
  - Eliminated React Flow warnings by memoizing `nodeTypes` and `edgeTypes`.
  - Fixed canvas freezes and click timeouts by using a `useRef` for the active `nodes` array inside the canvas change handlers, preventing callback recreation on every render.
  - Removed unused `pillPath` helper from `canvas-node.tsx` and cleaned up Tailwind styling overrides to use standard `postfix!` notation.
- [x] Canvas ergonomics: zoom controls, undo/redo, and keyboard shortcuts (feature-spec `17-canvas-ergonomics`)
  - Created `components/editor/canvas-control-bar.tsx` â€” pill-shaped floating control bar positioned bottom-left with zoom in/out, fit view, undo, and redo buttons. Disabled states are visually dimmed.
  - Created `hooks/use-keyboard-shortcuts.ts` â€” listens for `+`/`=` (zoom in), `-` (zoom out), `Cmd/Ctrl+Z` (undo), `Cmd/Ctrl+Shift+Z` (redo), `Cmd/Ctrl+Y` (redo). Ignores shortcuts while typing in inputs, textareas, or contentEditable elements.
  - Wired Liveblocks `useUndo`, `useRedo`, `useCanUndo`, `useCanRedo` hooks into the collaborative canvas.
  - Wired React Flow instance zoom methods (`zoomIn`, `zoomOut`, `fitView`) with smooth 300ms animations.
  - Build passes without type errors.

